---- Changes since 1.130 ----
Added the ability to manage groups too, and to specify which users and groups from the password file are allowed.
---- Changes since 1.180 ----
Added the ability to specify extra directives to be added to .htaccess files, thanks to Charlie Garrison <charlie@make-tracks.com.au>
---- Changes since 1.320 ----
Added a configuration option to deny users the ability to add or edit protected directories.
---- Changes since 1.380 ----
Added a Module Config option to set permissions on created .htaccess and .htpasswd files, which defaults to 644.
---- Changes since 1.500 ----
The list of allow directories for users can now include variables like $USER and $GROUP.
